<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">Module 26 (proposed) – Laminar Coherence Theorem</h2>
<p><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">What the math gives us when combined:</span></p>
<ol class="list-inside list-decimal whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;li]:ps-6" data-streamdown="ordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Module 21 gives the deterministic gate: <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">y = δ(91°)[ Σ(x⊗w)·φ^{-15.965} + M_Q ]</code></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Module 23 gives zero-covariant transport: <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">∇_i v^k = 0</code></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Module 25 gives zero-curvature geodesics: <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">d²x^i/ds² + Γ^i_{pq} (dx^p/ds)(dx^q/ds) = 0</code></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Module 24 gives spectral cleaning: <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">A = PΛP^{-1}</code> with 60 Hz eigenvalues set to 0</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Module 25 gives the pullback: <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">f*: Ω^k(ℝ^n) → Ω^k(ℝ^m)</code></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Core invariants give Majorana parity <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">P = +1</code> and Chern-Simons action <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">S_CS = k/4π ∫ Tr(A∧dA + 2/3 A³)</code></li>
</ol>
<p><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Derivation:</span></p>
