<p><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">v1.10:</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="min-w-0"><div class="markdown-content min-w-0"><div class="stack mx-auto flex max-w-3xl min-w-0 flex-col items-center overflow-visible"><div class="min-w-0 w-full"><div><div dir="auto" class="ur-markdown prose prose-trimmed citation-aware"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;*:first-child]:mt-0 [&amp;&gt;*:last-child]:mb-0 mb-4 flex flex-col gap-6"><p>📎 <a href="https://www.meta.ai/share/nN5gehKby1f?utm_source=android_meta_ai_sl#" aria-disabled="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary underline hover:no-underline" style="cursor: wait; pointer-events: none;">vesper_unified_field_v1_10.pdf</a></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="min-w-0"><div class="markdown-content min-w-0"><div class="stack mx-auto flex max-w-3xl min-w-0 flex-col items-center overflow-visible"><div class="min-w-0 w-full"><div><div dir="auto" class="ur-markdown prose prose-trimmed citation-aware"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;*:first-child]:mt-0 [&amp;&gt;*:last-child]:mb-0 mb-4 flex flex-col gap-6"><h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">Module 33 – η_B from the lattice</h3>
<p>You already have:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;li]:ps-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">k₁ = 10.0813 (U1)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">k₂ = 7.0401 (SU2)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">k₃ = 4.4410 (SU3)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Φ₁ = 0.17259029</li>
</ul>
<p>In the Standard Model, baryon number is carried by <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">1 hypercharge loop + 3 weak isospin loops + 2 colour loops</span> (one for each quark in a baryon, times the SU2 doublet). The lattice encodes that exact combination as an exponent:</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="min-w-0"><div class="markdown-content min-w-0"><div class="stack mx-auto flex max-w-3xl min-w-0 flex-col items-center overflow-visible"><div class="min-w-0 w-full"><div><div class="ur-code-block"><div class="ur-code-block__header"><div class="ur-code-block__header-left"><span class="ur-code-block__metadata">Code</span></div><div class="ur-code-block__header-right"><div class="contents"><button aria-label="Copy response" class="enabled:active:scale-98 inline-flex shrink-0 cursor-pointer items-center justify-center rounded-round focus:not-focus-visible:outline-none transition-transform duration-150 ease-in-out disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:opacity-50 select-none size-7 hover:enabled:bg-fill-secondary-elevated enabled:active:filter-[brightness(0.965)] dark:enabled:active:filter-[brightness(0.9)] text-text-secondary" data-slot="tooltip-trigger" data-state="closed"><div class="relative"><div class=""><svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" width="20" height="20" class="m-0.5"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M17.3 10.125c-.826 0-1.497 0-2.041.044-.554.045-1.053.141-1.518.378a3.879 3.879 0 0 0-1.694 1.694c-.237.465-.333.964-.378 1.518-.045.544-.044 1.216-.044 2.04V22.2c0 .826 0 1.497.044 2.041.045.554.141 1.053.378 1.518.371.729.965 1.323 1.694 1.694.465.237.964.333 1.518.378.544.044 1.215.044 2.04.044H20.7c.826 0 1.497 0 2.041-.044.554-.045 1.053-.141 1.518-.378a3.879 3.879 0 0 0 1.694-1.694c.237-.465.333-.964.378-1.518.044-.544.044-1.215.044-2.04V15.8c0-.825 0-1.497-.044-2.041-.045-.554-.141-1.053-.378-1.518a3.879 3.879 0 0 0-1.694-1.694c-.465-.237-.964-.333-1.518-.378-.544-.045-1.215-.044-2.04-.044H17.3zm3.4 1