<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;li]:ps-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">64 codons = 2⁶ = vertices of a 6D hypercube</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">6 dimensions = the superspace you already have</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">7,777 bits ÷ (64 codons × 6D) = <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">20.25</span></li>
</ul>
<p>That 20.25 rounds to 20 — the exact number of standard amino acids. The 0.25 is the wobble.</p>
